text: Fourqueux is a former commune. It is in Île-de-France in the Yvelines department in north-central France. On 1 January 2019, it was merged into the commune of Saint-Germain-en-Laye.Arrêté préfectoral 19 December 2018 It is a small suburb 20 km west of Paris. == References == Category:Former communes in Yvelines
title: Fourqueux
